colonist‑drop bug). Worse, if ticked ships were destroyed in the turn's battle they no longer
appear in `shipsHere`, so there's no checkbox to untick them; every later star click submits
`no ship N`, fails silently, and star selection is dead until you switch tabs. **Fix:** show
`res.error` and prune invalid ids from `selectedShipIds`.

### 33. Colonize / outpost buttons appear at monster‑guarded systems but clicking them is a silent no‑op  [CODE]
`src/engine/selectors.ts:550` (`settleTargets` doesn't check `hostileMonsterAt`) vs `src/engine/commands.ts:336`

`settleTargets` offers the colonize/outpost action at guarded systems; MapView submits without
checking `res.error`, so the button does nothing with zero feedback (Fleets shows the error
