### 35. Entering the Battle Lab mid‑game unmounts the whole GameShell → battle prompts unreachable  [VERIFIED]
`src/ui/App.svelte:47‑57` routes `#battle-lab` above the game screen; `Empires.svelte`/`Designer.svelte` set the hash mid‑game

