### 36. Leaving a game leaks its reports, replays, and an open battle viewer into the next game  [CODE]
`src/ui/state.svelte.ts:109‑126` — `leaveGame` resets only screen/chat/version

`app.reports`, `app.replays`, and `app.viewing` persist across `leaveGame`. Start a new solo
